\f0\fs24 \cf0 \b Age:\b0  32\
\
\b Appearance:\b0  Tall and angular, dark hair cut short. Grey eyes. Dresses plainly\'97dark trousers, worn boots, a canvas jacket she has owned for years. A thin scar on her left wrist from a childhood fall.\
\
\b Background:\b0  Grew up in Sainte-Barbe, the daughter of a fisherman and a schoolteacher. Left at twenty-five for the capital, where she worked as a translator of technical documents. Never married.\
\
\b Motivation:\b0  To understand why she left and whether she can belong somewhere again.\
\
\b Fears:\b0  That the village has moved on without her. That her mother will not forgive her silence.}